{
  "stem": "27335.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a sort of an accidental-- and I think I have to determine just how-- how-- how it happened, since I was-- I was an organizer, a full-time organizer in western-- in western Canada for an organization, cultural organization, that, see, benefit organization, and in the meantime being a member of the Communist Party, you see, where you are always organized.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, it-- it wasn't so-- so open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were also organizing that-- a function of in this leftist organization where almost all the members of the-- of the Communist Party, you see.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why we were so-- so effective.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are leading the great, great struggle in the hungry thirties, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It went down in history as the hungry thirties.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- it was our job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I came down for the convention.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was called down from my central office to help to organize that-- that convention in October.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And arrived-- arrived here on the-- on the 30th of-- 30th of August and was on a Saturday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The exhibition was still on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They showed me-- took me out to the exhibition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That was the last day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was an exhibition on a Sunday at-- at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So the-- the-- the day passed, and I got acquainted with a few of the leading-- the leading people in Hungarian-- Hungarian organization because they had a club here and they took me in the-- in the evening.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then Sunday passed and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Monday morning, I was going down to the editorial office of our paper, The Canadian-Hungarian [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden in a street corner and an intersection there's somebody's calling my name.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't-- who could be calling me in-- in-- Toronto here?",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
